KNOWN ISSUES: No Audio is available; Not Easy Configuration: After instalation/update of the addon, you must download this file https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp/blob/master/yt_dlp/extractor/viki.py and place it in ...kodi/addons/script.module.youtube.dl/lib/youtube_dl/extractor directory! Youtube-dl has not yet fixed the viki extractor, but the yt-dlp fork is. If after all this addon still doesn't work for you, use the official VIKI apps for your platform.
